channel.title: Comments on: Urban Decay Electric Pressed Pigment Palette Review and Looks!

item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description: Hot damn these colors look gorgeous on you! I think this one's going to be a skip for me thanks for my incredibly pale skin, but you know how to do a bold color right. The cobalt look is my favorite...and I can't wait to see what you come up with for the red.
item.content:encoded: Hot damn these colors look gorgeous on you! I think this one’s going to be a skip for me thanks for my incredibly pale skin, but you know how to do a bold color right. The cobalt look is my favorite…and I can’t wait to see what you come up with for the red.
